comments.body: I don't know how this really killed Dogecoin, yeah but today I've witnessed one of the largest actions occurring on $TOKEN as soon as it got listed on Bitget hours ago. The fact that it's associated Floki entices me. It could be an opportunity to invest once the market undergoes a correction. I imagine their primary objective being to tokenize and simplify the process of bringing real-life assets onto the blockchain. A whopping 1 trillion plus assets prepared for transfer to the platform.
